  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download VAIL and experience the #1, highest-rated VR shooter, with precision-crafted gunplay, stunning visuals, and a constantly expanding world of modes, maps, and community.     </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                       </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/5d6e9791da9467793c67a37745d79c6e.poster.avif?t=1772824603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/5d6e9791da9467793c67a37745d79c6e.webm?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/5d6e9791da9467793c67a37745d79c6e.mp4?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTRACTION (FREE EARLY ACCESS)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend into the depths of Reyn to extract encrypted data, technology, and resources while autonomous drones guard it like archangels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/82fdfe7fba091a5ac34016c84aa79fad.poster.avif?t=1772824603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/82fdfe7fba091a5ac34016c84aa79fad.webm?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRAINING GROUNDS (FREE-TO-PLAY)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in non-stop action on four free-to-play maps designed to improve skill with weapon pickups and loadout modifiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/c480777252c003c9fb29880ef063b0df.poster.avif?t=1772824603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/c480777252c003c9fb29880ef063b0df.webm?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/c480777252c003c9fb29880ef063b0df.mp4?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOCIAL HUB (FREE-TO-PLAY)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge others to intense 1v1 battles, get the best score in mini-golf, and unlock VAIL Combat or other rewards by extracting ORE shards from the quarry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/dc78112b4663969f62d0de76b218f41b.poster.avif?t=1772824603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/dc78112b4663969f62d0de76b218f41b.webm?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/dc78112b4663969f62d0de76b218f41b.mp4?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VAIL COMBAT (DLC)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain full access to VAIL's complete experience. Dominate in popular team-based and free-for-all game modes as you level up, unlock rewards, and top the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/7e43f232b022854724be1dd4db3cac22.poster.avif?t=1772824603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/7e43f232b022854724be1dd4db3cac22.webm?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/7e43f232b022854724be1dd4db3cac22.mp4?t=1772824603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRITICALLY ACCLAIMED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras/15fd0e6c61fa8d9b025a4ed44c909fda.avif?t=1772824603\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801550/extras_big/15fd0e6c61fa8d9b025a4ed44c909fda.avif?t=1772824603 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the party!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
